casebody.data:
John DOE, petitioner,
v.
BOARD OF COUNTY COMMISSIONERS OF PAYNE COUNTY, OKLAHOMA, et al. No. 15-387. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 11, 2016.

Motion of The Iraq and Afghanistan Veterans of America for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Tenth Circuit denied.
